    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CORRUPT
      Signifies that a policy has failed installation or withdrawal, but still hold some or all of its resources.
      FAILED
      Signifies that a policy has failed compilation and that it cannot be satisfied by the network at this time.
      INSTALL_REQ
      Signifies that a policy is to be installed or reinstalled.
      INSTALLED
      Signifies that a policy has been successfully installed.
      PURGED
      Signifies that a policy has been purged from the system.
      WITHDRAW_REQ
      Signifies that a policy will be withdrawn.
      WITHDRAWN
      Signifies that a policy has been withdrawn from the system.
